{"tid":1466843,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請將矛頭指向機管局","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:08.000Z","uid":74091,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52c57b761b033eac7362f46ebe0e6df3eeb6275c","tid":1466843,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:47.000Z","msg":"第一，機管局明知示威者塞住入唔到都唔cancel，係佢地行政有問題，明知入唔到點解比人check in? 預早講cancel就唔洗咁多旅客係到燥。<br />\n<br />\n第二，職員係有方法(職員通道/明星隧道)唔洗經我地塞既地方入到禁區，職員冇主動提供協助解決問題，係佢地既問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將矛頭指向機管局<br />\n係佢地既問題</span>"},{"pid":"f15088f98b8e0ce9c74a5e8a7cfbf1f7da9d07f5","tid":1466843,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"336844e954f1fa964a662e3b0bc878fb3b16bcc8","tid":1466843,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"811 721 612"},{"pid":"dead0357fcf0f6c097cbcb11068b0f60da4149c1","tid":1466843,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3244a7c54c982f90c4534a28e330984774a370","tid":1466843,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6d21ccc3b8a8d4f154b40c70e8286a7d179d51","tid":1466843,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"負皮既出黎講2句"},{"pid":"54ff764efac3dcbac689a2cd1e78da62901a4660","tid":1466843,"uid":41853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:59.000Z","msg":"你塞住條路大大聲同佢人地唔關我事，你怪機管局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">弱智兒童快樂無窮</span>"},{"pid":"85ad8379603116e793e1f63180